BWA use its own index set. To create the new genome index

Usage: bwa index genome.fa 

and add the entries in "bwa_index.loc". Please make sure that the 
fields are tab delimited, not space delimited, and have no trailing or 
extra whitespace (this is easy to slip in by accident). 

Place the .loc file under $GALAXY_PATH/tool-data/

Add the table details to main "tool_data_table_conf.xml" to get load the
built-in index in the BWA interface. 

support [at] oqtans.org 
